 * @param {array} otherArray The array whose values will be put into the base array.
 * This array is not modified by calling this function.
 * 
 * @return {array} Returns the base array (for chaining convenience).
 * 
 * @example
 * 
 * ```
 * let x = [1, -1, -2, 3];
 * replaceArray(x, ["a", "b"]);
 * console.log(x); // ["a", "b"]
